# Cloudflare Pages redirects for daminiestate.ae

# Old single-page anchors → new clean URLs
/index.html        /                301

# Map the former on-page sections to their new pages
/home              /                301
/listings          /properties/     301
/listing           /properties/     301

# Browsers probe /favicon.ico by default → point them at our SVG favicon
/favicon.ico       /favicon.svg     301

# Internal docs (CLAUDE.md / docs/) are reference-only — not public on the site
/docs/*            /404.html        404

# Trailing-slash convention is canonical (Cloudflare Pages serves /about/ from /about/index.html)
